1.   configuration properties --> VC++ Directories --> include directories 
add below location 
opencv_path\Documents\opencv\build\include

(if you find difficult please acess screen shot help)

2.   configuration properties --> VC++ Directories-->library directories 
add below location
openCV_path\Documents\opencv\build\x64\vc16\lib

(if you find difficult please acess screen shot help)

note:: no further setting is needed . this is enough because we are using a directive linker directly to access debug file . so no need to make nay change
